   Technology:
   Apple, Adobe
   Reach Accord
   On Software
   ----
   By Carrie Dolan
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/21/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
